'''木星極光紅外成像儀'''（Jovian Infrared Auroral Mapper，JIRAM）是前往[[木星|木星]]的[[朱諾號|朱諾號]]太空船攜帶，由義大利提供的影像[[光譜儀|光譜儀]]<ref name=wisc>[http://juno.wisc.edu/spacecraft_instruments_JIRAM.html WISC - The Jupiter InfraRed Auroral Mapper] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303182553/http://juno.wisc.edu/spacecraft_instruments_JIRAM.html |date=2016-03-03 }}</ref>。在歐洲太空總署（ESA）的[[羅塞塔號|羅塞塔號]]、[[金星特快車|金星特快車]]、和[[卡西尼－惠更斯號|卡西尼－惠更斯號]]任務都有類似的儀器<ref name=wisc/>。JIRAM的主要目標是使用波長在2-5μm之間的影像光譜儀研究木星上層大氣層直至氣壓為5-7帕（72-102磅/平方英寸）深處的大氣層<ref name=wisc/> Jupiter's "hot spots" and auroral regions are targeted for study.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18680411 |title=Adriani A, et al. - IRAM, the image spectrometer in the near infrared on board the Juno mission to Jupiter (2008) - Astrobiology |accessdate=2015-08-22 |archive-date=2016-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160427165215/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18680411 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

它希望描繪出{{chem|H|3|+}}離子、氨和磷化氫的分布<ref>[http://books.google.com/books?id=8HIrh-9o2CkC&pg=PA352&lpg=PA352&dq=Juno+JIRAM&source=bl&ots=S3rnksMskI&sig=s8uwqsFgx1PGUnGiSyxcy9plqXI&hl=en&sa=X&ei=NQAlUI7LEIqm9ATg0YCQDw&ved=0CDUQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=Juno%20JIRAM&f=false P. Irwin - '''Giant Planets of Our Solar System: Atmospheres, Composition, and Structure''' (2009) - Page 352]</ref>。{{chem|H|3|+}}的氫在地球上非常罕見，但是在宇宙中是非常普通的離子，稱為[[三氫陽離子|氫分子合質子]]或[[三氫陽離子|三氫陽離子]]<ref name="Carrington">{{cite journal
